Okay, in the morning I can.
*responds to Poy* Great, Poy! Scott would love to take you to Ton Ton Katsuya for brunch on New Year's Day morning. Does that work well for you? I'm happy to get the details finalized.
Wonderful, Poy. I'll let Scott know you're available for the New Year's Day brunch date at Ton Ton Katsuya. Thank you, and have a great rest of your day!
*after Poy responds* Oh, I see. No problem, Poy. Thank you for your time, and I hope you have a wonderful rest of your day.
